    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. when u say \"force accountability in an era of unchecked corporate power,\" it sounds like you're leans towards the regulatory side. isn't there a valid concern that these kinds of investigations are just being used by politicians to score points, and could actually end up hurting the economy by slowing down the tech sector?",
